注内存占用&#xff0c;所以不用左偏树。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skew_heap\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skew_heap</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leftist_tree\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leftist_tree</a></p>\n<p></p>"}], "type": "note", "tags": ["2018", "lecture16", "student", "unanswered"], "tag_good": [{"role": "student", "name": "Jiaao Ho", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": null, "id": "izb0cbqbyzd6wf", "photo_url": null, "published": true, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}], "unique_views": 123, "children": [{"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "no_upvotes": 0, "subject": "<p>左偏树要对 size 进行判断和维护, 而斜堆是合并后直接交换. 在树高大致相当时, 斜堆的时间复杂度的常数也比较小.</p>", "created": "2017-04-21T07:42:34Z", "bucket_order": 161, "bucket_name": "Week 4/16 - 4/22", "type": "followup", "tag_good": [], "uid": "izb0cbqbyzd6wf", "children": [{"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "subject": "<p>在操作系统里使用均摊复杂度是不是会产生一些问题呢</p>", "created": "2017-04-21T07:54:47Z", "bucket_order": 161, "bucket_name": "Week 4/16 - 4/22", "type": "feedback", "tag_good": [], "uid": "ie7xy5cvsc61qg", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "id": "j1rjj0q2m5752o", "updated": "2017-04-21T07:54:47Z", "config": {}}, {"anon": "no", "folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": null}, "subject": "<p>操作系统属于偏向实际应用的场景. 个人认为只要每次操作的时候时间开销都不太大就可以接受了.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>构造出让斜堆单次效率较高的数据特征较难构造 (参考卡splay), 实用场景下可认为都是随机数据, 被卡的几率较小.</p>", "created": "2017-04-22T06:37:18Z", "bucket_order": 161, "bucket_name": "Week 4/16 - 4/22", "type": "feedback", "tag_good": [], "uid": "izb0cbqbyzd6wf", "children": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "id": "j1sw78vs7om2id", "updated": "2017-04-22T06:37:18Z", "config": {}}], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "j1rj3bqy5cxja", "updated": "2017-04-21T07:42:34Z", "config": {}}], "tag_good_arr": ["izb0cbqbyzd6wf"], "id": "j1rfvrdbksg5xc", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": fals